						               													<description>Two players command ingenious fleets, bold captains, &amp;amp; fantastic monsters in an attempt to outmaneuver their opponent and destroy their flagship!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Winds of Fortune is an epic adventure of naval strategy for 2 players!  Games generally last between 45-60 minutes. Players each take control of powerful fleets of awesome ships and vicious monsters in an attempt to outmaneuver their opponents&amp;rsquo; fleet and destroy their flagship to secure victory.  The game comes with 2 prebuilt faction decks as well as enough extra cards to build your own custom decks.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;My goal in designing Winds of Fortune was to create a card game that really felt like you were commanding a fleet of ships on the high seas.  By creating a maneuverability mechanic unlike any other card game, positioning your cards properly is of the utmost importance just like real naval battles. With the added ability to create your own decks and customize your own flagship, you can also take full advantage of infinite strategies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;--from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
